      <question id="q1">
         <body>
            <p>What is the sample space S in this case? In other words, what are all the possible outcomes in this case? (Use B for a boy and G for a girl).
            </p>
         </body>
         <short_answer id="A"/>
         <part>
            <response input="A" match="*" score="1"/>
            <explanation>
               <p>There are four possible outcomes in this case:</p>
               <p>B<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095123-0500"?>&#8212;<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095121-0500" content=" - "?>the
                  first child is a boy, and the couple stops having children.</p>
               <p>GB<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095138-0500"?>&#8212;<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095136-0500" content=" - "?>the
                  first child is a girl and the second is a boy, and then the couple stops having
                  children.</p>
               <p>GGB<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095144-0500"?>&#8212;<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095141-0500" content=" - "?>the
                  first and second child
                  <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095204-0500"?>are<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095202-0500" content="is a"?>
                  girl<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095206-0500"?>s<?oxy_insert_end?>
                  and the third is a boy, and the couple stops having children.</p>
               <p>GGG<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095148-0500"?>&#8212;<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T095146-0500" content=" - "?>all
                  three children are girls but the couple stops having children for financial
                  reasons.</p>
            </explanation>
         </part>
